Description:
On the side of the road you meet a heron with a group of fennecs. When you approach the heron says to you:

"Aren't they adorable? These little fellows are the best companion anyone could ever want. I've trained them myself!

I'm a little sad to part with them, but as a fennec enthusiast, I want you to see how wonderful they are. I can sell you a freshly tamed one for 400g, if you want one that is well trained it will cost you 800g".
DescriptionAction: Do you want to buy a fennec?
